div.p:
Frequent Sailings from ALEXANDRIA to LIVERPOOL, also Regular Services
                            from LIVERPOOL to ALEXANDRIA and to ALGERIA, MALTA, LEVANT, BLACK SEA,
                            and other Mediterranean Ports.

To instal irrigation works, supplying the necessary plant for the purpose ;
                        to construct canals, drains, roads and tramways, and to carry on industries
                        connected with Agricultural enterprises.
